<bibRefCitation id="27961ADF285C23EC2D176DCDC03E4E83" author="Penttinen, J." editor="Rassi, P." journalOrPublisher="Ympaeristoeministerioe &amp; Suomen ympaeristoekeskus, Helsinki" pageId="0" pageNumber="1068" title="The 2010 Red List of Finnish Species" year="2010">Penttinen et al. 2010</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
